- Soldier's Tale | 4 | Action driven | Easiest of the six to read
- Detective's Tale | 2 | Nearly stopped | Still think it is the weakest section
- Scholar's Tale | 5 | Full arrival | Where the book's emotional intelligence lands

:NOW
Deciding whether to commit to The Fall of Hyperion next or let this one \
